4️⃣ Scenario-Based Questions — GS-Level
Scenario	How to Answer
“ML model suddenly predicts all transactions as fraud”	Check feature drift, version mismatch, or API payload errors. Roll back to last stable model version. Log and alert operations team.
“High latency in ML API”	Pre-load models, use async API, cache frequent requests, scale horizontally using multiple instances behind a load balancer.
“Integrate ML API with Portfolio Service”	Portfolio service sends features → ML API predicts fraud score → API returns structured JSON → Portfolio service decides action → log for audit.
“Stack use in production trading system”	Use stack for undoing last N trade operations, evaluating expressions in risk calculation, or backtracking failed order sequences.
“How to deploy ML API for thousands of requests/sec?”	Load balancing, async requests, pre-loaded models, caching, and monitoring latency & errors.
